Fladeby received the Amanda Award for Best Sound Design in 2008 for the movie O' Horten, and in 2015 for the movie Børning.
Petter Mads Fladeby (born April 1st 1961 in Denmark) is a sound designer and mixer working mainly in Norwegian films.
